{"tid":2156661,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺唔睇廢萌既人人品都唔會好得去邊","createTime":"2020-08-14T14:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T22:53:29.000Z","uid":4618,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd639948298495aef04e1af67111d847e2103d34","tid":2156661,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"諗返起讀中學個時，坐我隔離係個pat陰過晒眉既mk仔嚟。<br />\n<br />\n啱啱掉位個陣，佢懶親切咁同我吹水，佢話自己都有睇動漫，咁我問佢鍾意睇邊套啦，佢即刻就答鋼鍊，tvb夜晚播個陣個個禮拜都有追，雞啄唔斷咁講神作神作。<br />\n<br />\n然後佢問返我鍾意睇邊套，我答佢話今季點兔幾好睇，佢呆一呆跟住覆我話吓我唔睇呢啲廢萌㗎喎。我當堂唔想理佢，之後啲對話都係支吾應對。<br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐之後發現佢返學態度先極品，上堂永遠唔會帶文具，我永遠要預備多枝筆俾佢，但佢冇一次會還返俾我。<br />\n<br />\n小息放lunch個時成日有啲豬朋狗友嚟搵佢圍威喂，然後就會霸咗我個位坐，逼到我要自己縮埋喺角落睇書。<br />\n<br />\n睇呢啲小事都知佢係讀唔成書啦，聽講佢dse得10分，報咗讀ive fd冇幾耐就去咗考警隊，之後就再冇佢消息了。"},{"pid":"9d168f19a6b360bc884dbf202e61138eb89a7172","tid":2156661,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"鋼鍊係廢萌番？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec6aca35ed2f4c4180c0ef268616119ac6478de","tid":2156661,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d168f19a6b360bc884dbf202e61138eb89a7172","tid":2156661,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"鋼鍊係廢萌番？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"